highlights.text: “Addicted (feat. TIMID.)” by Naarly, Daytona, LEWS, FIRSTCLASS, and TIMID. is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs United Kingdom, up 16 spots at #59.
“The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs United Kingdom the longest, at 84 days straight.
